**list of dependencies:**
Installation of the following packages / libraries are needed to properly utilize TCB.

- python-openstackclient
- python-keystoneclient
- python-glanceclient
- python-novaclient
- python-neutronclient
- python-cinderclient
- python-swiftclient
- python-bugzilla
- lauchpadlib
- behave
- python-jenkins
- gerritlib
- httplib2  (I’ve run into scenarios where I needed to make my own REST call)
- libvirt-python (because I need direct access to libvirt for nova tests)
- untangle (to easily map XML to python dicts)
- pyyaml (because I’m sure someone will need config files)
- toolz  (strictly not necessary, but a good idea.  Provides functional python)
- pyrsistent  (as above, providing immutable data structures)
- mypy-lang  (recommendation for python3+.  optional static type checking)